### CCR-013 §4, §5 — GET metadata + PATCH with If-Match ETag
###
### 검증:
### - GET metadata 응답에 ETag 헤더
### - PATCH with stale ETag → 412 Precondition Failed
### - PATCH with current ETag → 200 OK + new ETag
### - JSON Merge Patch (RFC 7396) 동작

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}
@skin_id = sk_01HVQK-test

### 21.1 GET /api/v1/skins/{id}/metadata — 초기 조회
# @name getMetadata
GET {{host}}/api/v1/skins/{{skin_id}}/metadata
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK
# ETag: W/"3-xyz..."
# Content-Type: application/json
# {
#   "skin_name": "wsop-2026-test",
#   "version": "1.0.0",
#   "colors": { "badge_check": "#00FF00", ... },
#   ...
# }

### 21.2 PATCH /api/v1/skins/{id}/metadata — 정상 편집
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/skins/{{skin_id}}/metadata
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
If-Match: {{getMetadata.response.headers.ETag}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "colors": {
    "badge_check": "#00AA00"
  },
  "fonts": {
    "pot": {
      "size": 48
    }
  }
}

# 예상: 200 OK + 새 ETag + 갱신된 skin.json 전체

### 21.3 PATCH with stale ETag → 412 Precondition Failed
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/skins/{{skin_id}}/metadata
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
If-Match: W/"1-stale-etag"
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "skin_name": "wsop-2026-test-v2"
}

# 예상: 412 Precondition Failed
# {
#   "error": "ETAG_MISMATCH",
#   "current_etag": "W/\"5-...\"",
#   "message": "다른 세션이 먼저 수정했습니다. refetch 후 재시도하세요."
# }

### 21.4 PATCH — If-Match 헤더 누락
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/skins/{{skin_id}}/metadata
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "skin_name": "wsop-2026-no-etag"
}

# 예상: 428 Precondition Required (또는 400 Bad Request)

### 21.5 PATCH — 스키마 검증 실패 (색상 hex 아님)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/skins/{{skin_id}}/metadata
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
If-Match: {{getMetadata.response.headers.ETag}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "colors": {
    "badge_bet": "red"
  }
}

# 예상: 422 Unprocessable Entity
# { "error": "SCHEMA_VIOLATION", "path": "colors.badge_bet", "message": "..." }
